title: Kaapa
subTitle: When Anand finds his pregnant wife's name on Kerala's anti-social list alongside other criminals, he sets on a determined mission to clear her name and prove her innocence.

title: Laila O Laila
subTitle: After his post-graduate studies, Karthik takes a holiday in Europe. On his return journey, he falls in love at first sight with Nandana, and goes to great lengths to win her heart.

title: Time Machine
subTitle: When Elango and Pulivetti find a time machine, they decide to use it for their benefit. While meddling with time, they prevent a gangster's death and this lands them in trouble.

title: Mawali Raaj
subTitle: In order to obtain a family of their own, two young children of two single parents devise a plan to bring them together.

title: Dhruva
subTitle: A committed police officer, Dhruva, uncovers a web of organised crime headed by a scientist, Siddharth Abhimanyu. But when Dhruva tries to build a case against him, he faces many challenges.

title: Siren
subTitle: After serving 14 years in prison, a man is released on parole. As he tries to reconnect with his family, he vows revenge against those who wronged him.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: The Family Star
subTitle: Govardhan, a diligent architect, longs for a partner who understands his commitment to his large family. When Indu, a new tenant, moves in, his life starts to unfold in a new direction.

title: Gally Rowdy
subTitle: A young man tries to find a balance between his love interest and friends. Meanwhile, his friends convince him to stay rowdy.

title: Veer Madhakari Iss Sadi Ka
subTitle: Madakari, an honest cop, is killed by the hands of the atrocious Babji. Sathyaraju, who bears an uncanny resemblance to Madakari, takes his place to take care of his daughter amd exact revenge.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: Vijay, a dedicated police officer, is shattered to discover his brother Aftab is a ruthless criminal. Torn between duty and love, Vijay embarks on a relentless quest to bring him to justice.

title: Mohini
subTitle: Vaishnavi and Sandeep, a couple in love, are engaged to be married. However, things spiral out of control when she gets possessed by a lookalike who is thirsty for vengeance.

subTitle: Following his father's death, a man gives up on his dream to become a film-maker and joins the police force. He then attempts to track down a psychopathic killer who targets schoolgirls.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi
subTitle: A man and a woman develop a great bond after the latter arrives in Hyderabad. However, they realise their love for each other when the woman's marriage is arranged to a person of her parent's choice.

title: Power Unlimited 2
subTitle: Karthikeya, a man who is devoted to his family, faces a huge challenge as his violent and turbulent past begins to resurface.

title: Mission 118
subTitle: An investigative journalist has nightmares about a young woman's murder and tries to uncover whether his dreams have any connection to reality.

title: Bhagavanth Kesari
subTitle: A former prisoner is adamant about training his adoptive daughter to join the Indian Army. However, his mission is interrupted by a conflict with a ruthless businessman.

title: Geetanjali 2
subTitle: Sreenu receives a directorial offer from Vishnu to shoot in a bungalow. Later, him and his crew realise that Vishnu orchestrated the ploy to seek revenge by trapping them in a haunted house.

title: 24 Ghante In Chennai
subTitle: After a journalist is declared brain dead following an accident, his parents choose to donate his heart to a girl in urgent need. What follows is a high-stakes mission by a group of people to deliver the heart.

title: 24 Ghante In Chennai

title: Meri Saugandh
subTitle: Ramu loves Lakshmi, whose father is the chief of the village. In order to prove his love, Ramu must win a challenge posed by a rival village and beat Giridhar, who is also keen on marrying Lakshmi.

title: Das Ka Dhamki
subTitle: A financially struggling waiter's life drastically changes course when he learns of his rich lookalike, the CEO of a pharmaceutical company.

title: Bal Hanuman 2
subTitle: Bal Hanuman harmlessly misuses his natural gift while fighting demons and lands in trouble. Soon enough, he approaches Lord Sun in order to gain control over his superpowers.

title: Anjaniputra
subTitle: A businessman saves a policeman from a group of thugs. As a result, he incurs the wrath of a ruthless local gangster who is also an assassin.

title: Kumari Jille Ke Thugs
subTitle: Caught in the turmoil of prison life, a determined man forges alliances with fellow inmates, plotting a daring plan to escape and regain their freedom.

title: Kee
subTitle: Siddharth, a hacker who is blessed with a happy family, falls in love with a girl. However, his life changes drastically when he becomes a victim of cyberbullying that leads him to another hacker.

title: Yashoda
subTitle: Surrogate mother Yashodha is advised to follow a few guidelines to keep herself and her baby healthy and safe. However, something happens at the surrogate centre that puts both of them at risk.

title: Godfather
subTitle: The chief minister's passing wreaks havoc across the state and in his political party. However, a mysterious contender for the post rises to eradicate wrongdoers.

title: Kabali
subTitle: When Kabali raises his voice against the oppression faced by Tamil labourers in Malaysia, he is imprisoned for 25 years. After being released, he seeks revenge on the ones who wronged him.
